item.title: Universitat Pompeu Fabra: Architecture Pictures
item.description: Barcelona’s Universitat Pompeu Fabra has some truly amazing architecture at its Campus de la Ciutudella. From what I understand, I mostly discovered the Law Department and some Library building. All pictures are taken with my Google Pixel 4a 5G in Normal mode. 𝑓/2.2, ISO 101, t=1/25s, alt=Two buildings with a inner floor that has a large roof. The left building has a wooden design, the right one has a large glass front in which you can see some lecture halls.
